<h2 id="using-a-grid">Using a Grid</h2>

<p>The grid systems were made popular with the wave of Swiss Style graphic design. The point is to work creatively within the grid, but also break free when you need it.</p>

<p>Even a simple grid gives you a lot of variety in placing your content. You use the modules as basis for larger content areas. This creates alignment and balance in your design.</p>

<p><a href="http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled1-e4c6bc43aede06582e6ef0ee262ccf45_large.jpg"><img src="http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled1-e4c6bc43aede06582e6ef0ee262ccf45_medium.jpg" srcset="http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled1-e4c6bc43aede06582e6ef0ee262ccf45_medium.jpg 800w, http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled1-e4c6bc43aede06582e6ef0ee262ccf45_large.jpg 1440w" sizes="600px" /></a></p>

<p><a href="http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled2-3981a632743ce8f6d4c7fecfca5ca133_large.jpg"><img src="http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled2-3981a632743ce8f6d4c7fecfca5ca133_medium.jpg" srcset="http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled2-3981a632743ce8f6d4c7fecfca5ca133_medium.jpg 800w, http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled2-3981a632743ce8f6d4c7fecfca5ca133_large.jpg 1440w" sizes="600px" /></a></p>

<p><a href="http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled3-afa545ef29c935df230aabed22abb7bc_large.jpg"><img src="http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled3-afa545ef29c935df230aabed22abb7bc_medium.jpg" srcset="http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled3-afa545ef29c935df230aabed22abb7bc_medium.jpg 800w, http://assets.runemadsen.com/grid_modular_filled3-afa545ef29c935df230aabed22abb7bc_large.jpg 1440w" sizes="600px" /></a></p>

