<h2 id="karl-gerstners-flexible-grid">Karl Gerstner’s Flexible Grid</h2>

<p>Even though it’s quite some years ago now, Karl Gerstner is one of the few graphic designers who approached grid design from a programmable point of view.</p>

<p><a href="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner0-ceb08c88df5b3ec498c08938ba8fbde5_large.jpg"><img src="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner0-ceb08c88df5b3ec498c08938ba8fbde5_medium.jpg" srcset="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner0-ceb08c88df5b3ec498c08938ba8fbde5_medium.jpg 800w, http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner0-ceb08c88df5b3ec498c08938ba8fbde5_large.jpg 1440w" sizes="600px" /></a></p>

<p><a href="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner1-39a016020da69cdfde89178c35ac7017_large.jpg"><img src="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner1-39a016020da69cdfde89178c35ac7017_medium.jpg" srcset="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner1-39a016020da69cdfde89178c35ac7017_medium.jpg 800w, http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner1-39a016020da69cdfde89178c35ac7017_large.jpg 1440w" sizes="600px" /></a></p>

<p><a href="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner2-b35ac37eddc492709b484b3713eaa8c7_large.jpg"><img src="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner2-b35ac37eddc492709b484b3713eaa8c7_medium.jpg" srcset="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner2-b35ac37eddc492709b484b3713eaa8c7_medium.jpg 800w, http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner2-b35ac37eddc492709b484b3713eaa8c7_large.jpg 1440w" sizes="600px" /></a></p>

<p><a href="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner3-b692262b635861612a56945393706e30_large.jpg"><img src="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner3-b692262b635861612a56945393706e30_medium.jpg" srcset="http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner3-b692262b635861612a56945393706e30_medium.jpg 800w, http://assets.runemadsen.com/gerstner3-b692262b635861612a56945393706e30_large.jpg 1440w" sizes="600px" /></a></p>

